window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>John Farrell is about to get \"The Cure\". Old age can never kill him now. The only problem is, everything else still can. </p> <p>Imagine a near future where a cure for aging is discovered and - after much political and moral debate - made available to people worldwide. Immortality, however, comes with its own unique problems, including evil green people, government euthanasia programs, a disturbing new religious cult, and other horrors. </p> <p>Witty, eerie, and full of humanity, <i>The Postmortal</i> is an unforgettable thriller that envisions a pre-apocalyptic world so real that it is completely terrifying.</p>"; 
